# Copilot Instructions
# Follow the repository's conventions:
# 
# 1. Use GitHub MCP Server to manage GitHub topics (issues, PRs)
# 2. Branch naming: <type>/<description> 
#    Types: feature, bugfix, hotfix, release, chore, refactor, docs
# 3. PR format: #<issue-number> - <title>
# 4. ALWAYS create branch before working on issue
#
# For full instructions see: .github/copilot-instructions.md
